issue.title: Collision with Tilemap background
issue.body:
The Tilemap provided for our background has the potential to be used with collision against players.
Once we're using the `Arcade` physics system, implement tilemap collision.

issue.title: Export calculation to the server
issue.body:
Where possible, we should be exporting as much as we can to the game server instead of client-side.
This includes player and enemy location-calculating, or at the very least, location validation.
